{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070210/extras/welcome_box.png?t=1735228847\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fame is a visual novel that takes place in a hotel where a bunch of guests have been invited to attend a special week-long event hosted by hotel CEO Mr. Sasha Manson. However, things in the hotel start to take a turn for the worse when attendants start being murdered by an unknown killer. As the player it is your job to seek out the killer amongst the group or potential staff. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While you are uncovering the truth you will need to compete against the detective on the scene who believes that you are the murderer. With multiple choice actions the ending will always be different. So be careful about what you do! It might cost you everything in the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070210/extras/what_to_expect.png?t=1735228847\" />The story of Fame is changed based on the actions you make during the game; each action has its own consequences that will impact your ending later on. Fame contains the following content: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Choice Matters Gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Main Story </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 7 Different Endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 1 Side Story Included Free (Coming Soon)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Snaps allow you to replay certain scenes (18+ filter will hide this option in the menu)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070210/extras/meet_the_cast.png?t=1735228847\" />Fame has 7 characters that each have their own unique personality &amp; have a more realistic perspective on what's happening around them. Meet them &amp; get to know them over time in game before the horrors unfold. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Mr. Sasha Manson</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Charlotte Morris</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Jade Cooper</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Ashlee Liv</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Zoe MacLean</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Phoebe Grace</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Detective Hellen Paryss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> You!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070210/extras/side_story.png?t=1735228847\" />Fame will have a total of 4 side stories that will release over the course of time. 1 side story will come with the base game &amp; will be free. Characters from the main story may make appearances or some new faces will join in for a new story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070210/extras/dev_notes.png?t=1735228847\" />Fame is not at all a sexual focused game. The game contains some adult scenes with nudity but does not set that as the main focus of the story. If you are not interested in seeing these sexual scenes you can enable the 18+ Content filter in the options menu. This will stop you from picking any actions in the story that will lead to anything sexual that contains nudity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some features may need more time to be developed &amp; will not be enabled in the Demo or full game.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Friends!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/a